message.body: It's getting a little chillier. You might make a few dollars tonight!
We shall see. I'm already here and I did not bring a big coat.
Oh no you wouldn't. I'm not a nice person when I'm cold!
So almost normal you then?
Yes, but worse.
Look at this face. So adorable! http://imgur.com/fDNmoWS
Ehhh...
Too dark?
I have nothing against it being dark.
And so it begins...
Goodluck!
Thanks. How's your night going?
Doing ok. I did back and shoulders at the gym. Protein bar and shake for dinner. Just lounging in bed for a bit before showering. Then fruit and tv!
Solid night.
Did you give them back to him?
I didn't have them.
I know. Lol. That's pretty funny that someone needs sunglasses at this hour
I told him to make good decisions tonight.
Hahah.
Lol. Good job Phuong.
Thank you for the approval Steve.
I approve of everything except rib jabs from you
Oh that's too bad cause they're my favorites.
I haven't flinched so much before lol
No better time than the present hahah.
Some drink girl just got up in my space.
*drunk
I told her that she couldn't be here and then security came.
People doing their job. Oh yeah. You cool?
I'm good. This is a young crowd, might be annoying.
Is the music decent at least?
ï¿¼
Can't tell from that =/ The bass just wrecks the recording quality.
And someone just lost their phone.
Sounds like a regular night out at the clubs
Yup.
Kids.
This kid is literally staring at me trying to guess how long ago I graduate ex
*graduated
I don't know much about being a girl fending off guys but I would imagine giving them no information is best
He was standing here waiting for me to text him. I walked away and Waite it out until he left.
*waited
Haha. Oh man. The awkward times. I do not miss them.
And a kid just threw up.
Another essential aspect heh
And now there's an Asian couple fighting in front of my counter.
These kids are a mess.
Haha. I hope things shape up in there
Really, a mess.
I hope it isn't in you to clean it up
On*
This is an interesting nights
*night
I'm sure it is. I wish mine ended on a more positive note.
What's wrong?
Related to Thuy and communication between myself and her other friends on the matter.
Okay. So I guess your other plans for the night fell through?

In midst of discussing what needs done for Thuy, her one friend has the notion I was trying to be condescending, because at a time like this I have it in me to be that guy. No I'm still situated in the apartment.
You're trying.
She said "I'd appreciate it if you weren't so condescending yo me. I'm removing myself from the chat. Goodnight."

Here's what I drafted in response but did not send: It's regretful you think I had the intent to be condescending. I'm just mentally and physically exhausted. As for today all I know is Thuy and Lauren went to dinner. I was told Ryan is on his way to Thuy. Beyond that I've nothing.
Lol I think there's a mosquito in the apartment. The hunt begins!
For now, why don't you just try to relax and watch something.
I've stopped participating in the chat. I told the one friend who's with her I approve of taking her to the ER.
And Moby Dick that mosquito!
Haha. Let's hope
Uyen's coming home tomorrow. Can't wait to see her! Even though it's only been 2 weeks lol
It feels longer!
That's what she said
I haven't found the mosquito and am hoping I just heard things. Feeling rather sleepy.
Hahah go to sleep.
It's disgusting here tonight.
And there are cops outside.
They're getting ready for the 2 am madness.
I hope you'll be able to join us tomorrow :) Saturday too. Gonna have game night at Cindy's place. She miraculously has off on Saturday!
I'm gonna try to pass out for now. Gnite and I'll hope you get out without anyone spewing on you.
It's just gross, like I saw a girl get carried out of the bathroom by security.
I'm looking forward to brunch.
Hopefully it doesn't rain like this on Saturday!
Pancakes!
And French toast!
Ahhhhh hahahah!

So I was trying to send out that email to my boss bit realized I didn't have her contact information! So I tried finding it online. Couldn't find it. So I guessed it, and I guessed right on the second try!!! Mwaaaaahahahah!
I don't know if you're that excited or crazy from lack of sleep
But yay for the success!
Hey, I slept well!
I'm glad you were able to :)
Thanks. Happy Friday!!! Hope the day is going by quickly enough.
It is. Figure out what you're doing tonight?
Working.
Friday was never an issue.
I'm ready for nap time. Had a nice lunch at Sangkee duck house with co-workers
Oh yum! Good lunch. That's my mom's favorite restaurant.
Shared the dinner for 2 between 3 guys. Was delicious.
